</div>
<button class="accordion">What is the best treatment for sepsis?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>The best treatment for sepsis include:</p>
<li> Antibiotics. Treatment with antibiotics should begin immediately</li>
<li> Intravenous fluids. People who have sepsis receive intravenous fluids right away, usually within three hours</li>
<li> Vasopressors.</li><p></p>
